OL,3,CSister of murder victim on 'finding
OL,4,Clight' again after her brother's death
OL,6,FThe sister of a man who was stabbed to
OL,7,Fdeath in Cornwall says his legacy will
OL,8,Fbe protecting others from knife crime.
OL,10,FMichael Riddiough-Allen, known as
OL,11,FMike, was killed outside a nightclub
OL,12,Fin Bodmin in 2023. He was an innocent
OL,13,Fbystander who was fatally stabbed as
OL,14,Fhe tried to break up a fight.
OL,16,FJake Hill, 25, was jailed for life for
OL,17,FMike's murder and injuring four
OL,18,Fothers, and ordered to to serve a
OL,19,Fminimum of 28 years in prison.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
