FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777475480
OL,3,CSister of murder victim on 'finding
OL,4,Clight' again after her brother's death
OL,6,FMike, a popular local rugby player and
OL,7,Fcar enthusiast was only 32 when he
OL,8,Fdied. Now his family hold educational
OL,9,Ftalks aimed to warn people of the
OL,10,Fdangers of knife crime.
OL,12,FMike's sister Becky Dustan says this
OL,13,Fis still a very hard time of year for
OL,14,Fall of his family and friends.
OL,16,FShe told ITV News: ''I have found over
OL,17,Fthe years that things don't get any
OL,18,Feasier, they just get different. This
OL,19,Fweek especially is quite difficult for
OL,20,Fus, but we do have little things that
OL,21,Fwe do to keep Mike in the forefront.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777475480
OL,3,CSister of murder victim on 'finding
OL,4,Clight' again after her brother's death
OL,6,F"On the anniversary, at 3am we will go
OL,7,Fto where he last fell. We will go and
OL,8,Fhave a bottle of Rattler and a pasty
OL,9,Fto celebrate all things Mike and just
OL,10,Fremember him for a moment.
OL,12,F"It's something I don't look forward
OL,13,Fto, but it is an important thing for
OL,14,Fme", she added.
OL,16,FBecky has channelled her energy into
OL,17,Fcampaign work, recently speaking at
OL,18,Fthe unveiling of the Knife Angel
OL,19,Fstatue in Plymouth.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777475480
OL,3,CSister of murder victim on 'finding
OL,4,Clight' again after her brother's death
OL,6,FThe family have also set up Mike's
OL,7,FTrust, an educational initiative aimed
OL,8,Fat reducing knife crime. Now Becky
OL,9,Fregularly goes into schools and
OL,10,Fcolleges talking to young people about
OL,11,Fthe dangers of carrying knives.
OL,13,FBecky says: "It is a free form of
OL,14,Ftherapy for me. I'm very lucky that I
OL,15,Fget to speak about Michael all the
OL,16,Ftime. It's a horrible story what
OL,17,Fhappened to him that I hope never
OL,18,Fhappens to anyone else. But we can use
OL,19,Fit in a positive way. We can find the
OL,20,Flight in that.''
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777475480
OL,3,CSister of murder victim on 'finding
OL,4,Clight' again after her brother's death
OL,6,F''The money we raise we put into other
OL,7,Forganisations to encourage young
OL,8,Fpeople to get involved in different
OL,9,Factivities and skills and find their
OL,10,Fown place in life, and to give some
OL,11,Fyoung people who are at risk of making
OL,12,Fpoor choices an opportunity to find a
OL,13,Fbetter path.''
OL,15,FEach summer the family hold a
OL,16,Ffundraising festival called Mike's
OL,17,FMotor Mania at Spitfire Field in
OL,18,FPerranporth to raise funds for Mike's
OL,19,FTrust. This year the event is being
OL,20,Fheld on Sunday 26th July.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777475480
OL,3,CSister of murder victim on 'finding
OL,4,Clight' again after her brother's death
OL,6,FBecky believes keeping Mike's name out
OL,7,Fthere is the best way she can honour
OL,8,Fhis memory.
OL,10,FShe says: ''We just want his legacy to
OL,11,Fbe that positivity. Even in the
OL,12,Fdarkest times, even in the worst
OL,13,Fsituations, there is always a little
OL,14,Fbit of light. And you can take a
OL,15,Freally terrible situation and make it
OL,16,Fsomething positive and something to be
OL,17,Flearned from.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777475480
OL,3,CSister of murder victim on 'finding
OL,4,Clight' again after her brother's death
OL,6,F"I want people to be able to look at
OL,7,Fus and go, yes, it is the most
OL,8,Fhorrific thing that can ever happen to
OL,9,Fyou and it breaks you. But I can build
OL,10,Fmyself up from this. I can move
OL,11,Fforward, and I can see the light going
OL,12,Fforward.''
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
